sourcesContent: import React, { Fragment } from 'react'; import {MDBProgress, MDBCol, MDBRow} from "mdbreact"; import "../Styles/dashboard.css"; const CardContent = (props) => { const {primary, secondary} = props.data; return( {primary.title} {primary.value} {primary.progress_title} {`(${primary.progress_value}) %`} {secondary.title} {secondary.value} {secondary.progress_title} {`(${secondary.progress_value}) %`} ); } export default CardContent;
